These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: coffee, fanta
City: miami, hannover
The people have 2 different jobs:  security-guard, police-officer
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: dannemann, blend
1. the blend-smoker is on the left or right of the police-officer##3
2. the person drinking fanta is in an even position##4
3. the person traveling to hannover is the person drinking coffee##1
4. the blend-smoker is on the right of the dannemann-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |
| Beverage      | coffee  | fanta   |
| City   | hannover     | miami   |
| Job         | police-officer | security-guard |
| Cigar     | dannemann | blend    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-2::.
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: aristoff, baccarat
The people have 2 different hobbies: reading, traveling
2 different pets are kept: dog, rat
There are 2 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, mirinda
1. the owner of the rat is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's hobby is reading is the person drinking mirinda##1
3. the baccarat-smoker is on the right of the person who's hobby is traveling##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |
| Cigar          | aristoff     | baccarat |
| Hobby   | traveling | reading  |
| Pet           | rat         | dog     |
| Beverage     | iced-tea   | mirinda    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-3::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, soy-milk
There 2 different types of food: broccoli, peas
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: alhambra, swisher
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: november, august
1. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left or right of the person eating peas##3
2. the swisher-smoker is on the right of the person eating peas##1
3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |       2       |
| Beverage    | soy-milk     | hot-chocolate |
| Food         | peas | broccoli    |
| Cigar         | alhambra         | swisher        |
| Birthday   | november         | august    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-4::.
