.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-6::.
2 different games are played: poker, scrabble
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: february, january
The people have 2 different hobbies: chess, baking
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: climbing, soccer
1. the person who's sport is soccer is in an even position##4
2. the person who's birthday is in january is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person playing scrabble is the person who's birthday is in february##1
4. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left of the person who's birthday is in january##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |
| Game           | scrabble | poker    |
| Birthday   | february       | january |
| Hobby           | chess         | baking    |
| Sport         | climbing    | soccer   |

