There are 2 different favourite colors: light-blue, orange
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: classical, trance
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: balloon-flower, sunflower
1. the fan of trance is in an odd position##4
2. the person who likes orange is on the left or right of the fan of classical##3
3. the person traveling to prague is on the left of the person who growsballoon-flower##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |
| City      | prague  | venice    |
| Color           | orange  | light-blue |
| Music-Genre   | trance | classical |
| Flower     | sunflower    | balloon-flower  |

