2 different brands of cigars are smoked: montecristo, prince
2 different games are played: billiard, canasta
House: ranch-style, townhouse
1. the prince-smoker is on the left of the person playing canasta##1
2. the person playing billiard is on the left or right of the person drinking water##3
3. the ranch-style house is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |    2     |
| Beverage    | hot-chocolate | water    |
| Cigar         | prince        | montecristo |
| Game         | billiard          | canasta     |
| House   | ranch-style        | townhouse     |

 